name: Uncanny Scorched
description: Artist: Vida V. | This is another one of the Uncanny Canvas skull series. The original TwoToJazz piece that is transferred to the skull was a piece that I made during the month long California fires in August-September 2020. This special skull features eyes also made in TwoToJazz. TwoToJazz is an iPad app developed by Vida | Creation Date: September 4, 2020 - April 29, 2021
